results.name: Number of ordered multiset partitions of integer partitions of n where the sequence of LCMs of the blocks is weakly increasing.
comment: If we form a multiorder by treating integer partitions (a,...,z) as multiarrows LCM(a,...,z) <= {z,...,a}, then a(n) is the number of triangles of weight n.
results.author: _Gus Wiseman_, Sep 07 2018
